Alfacam Raises 4 Million Euros From Fehervari, GIMV, Tijd Says

-- B y   A n d r e w   C l a p h a m
-- 
2011-04-18T06:31:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-18/alfacam-raises-4-million-euros-from-fehervari-gimv-tijd-says.html
Alfacam Group (ALFA)  NV raised 4 million
euros from its biggest shareholder Gabriel Fehervari and
investment firm  GIMV NV (GIMB) , De Tijd reported, citing the company.  The transaction comprises a cash injection of 3.2 million
euros and subordinated debt with warrants for 800,000 euros,
according to the newspaper. Fehervari, with 47.5 percent of the
company, provided almost half the amount raised, and the
remaining shares were bought by GIMV, the newspaper said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Clapham at 
 aclapham@bloomberg.net  